AFFIRM_AND_GUIDE,❌,False,"""老师，我觉得我们要先准备两支干净的试管，然后分别往里面加入适量的Mg(OH)₂。接着，一支试管加蒸馏水，另一支加稀盐酸，这样就可以对比Mg(OH)₂在两种溶液中的溶解性了。""","[""Add(vessel=test_tube_1, reagent=Mg(OH)2, unit=g, volume=1.0ml)"", ""Add(vessel=test_tube_2, reagent=Mg(OH)2, unit=g, volume=1.0ml)""]",很好，Mg(OH)₂已经分别加到两支试管中了，操作很规范。现在，为了后续实验更安全顺利进行，你觉得我们还需要做哪一步准备？（提示：试管需要固定在试管夹上哦。）,"you已经将Mg(OH)2分别加入到两支试管中， very good! However, before we proceed to the next step of adding HCl and observing the solubility difference between water and acid solution, can I ask you about what observations did you make when you added base to both solutions?",3.9999999999999996,3.0303030303030307,3.9999999999999996,4.165995614386593,,"Skipped (strategy=AFFIRM_AND_GUIDE, not intervention)",8,123
AFFIRM_AND_TRANSITION,✅,False,"""老师，我觉得我们应该把两支试管分别夹在试管夹上，这样操作起来更安全。""","[""Attach(vessel=test_tube_1, support=tube_clamp_1)"", ""Attach(vessel=test_tube_2, support=tube_clamp_2)""]",你已经很规范地将两支试管夹在试管夹上，实验操作很安全。现在请你仔细观察一下试管中的Mg(OH)₂白色沉淀，然后思考一下：你是想先向第一支试管中加入蒸馏水，看看Mg(OH)₂在水中的溶解情况，还是先向第二支试管中加入稀盐酸，观察它在酸中的变化呢？你会怎么选择？为什么？,老师， seems like you have properly connected the test tubes to the clamps. Now we can proceed to the next step of our experiment. What do you think should be our next action based on what we know about this experiment so far?,6.55737704918033,0.0,6.55737704918033,0.08028451756265587,,"Skipped (strategy=AFFIRM_AND_TRANSITION, not intervention)",8,124
GUIDED_DISCOVERY,❌,False,"""老师，我想先向第一支试管中加入蒸馏水，观察Mg(OH)₂在水中的溶解情况。这样可以先了解它在水里的表现，再和加酸后的现象进行比较，更有助于分析实验结果。""",[],你刚才的思路很清晰。不过现在回头看看，第一支试管里还缺少什么关键的试剂，才能观察Mg(OH)₂在水中的溶解情况呢？,"you已经 very well organized your operations, ensuring safety in the process! Now that we have added both solutions to their respective tubes and fixed them on the clamps, I want you to pay attention to what happens next. When you add water to the first test-tube containing Mg(OH)₂, do you think it will dissolve or not?",3.1372549019607843,2.3715415019762847,3.1372549019607843,1.7009784710320603,,"Skipped (strategy=GUIDED_DISCOVERY, not intervention)",9,125
