  你观察到试管中已经充满黄绿色的气体，这是氯气的颜色。现在覺得，如果玩家直接暴露在光下，甲烷和 chlorine 反应会发生在什么情况下？ still remember this reaction requires light for it to occur, particularly strong light can make the reaction happen faster and sometimes even go out of control. Sometimes using an aluminum foil around the test-tube is necessary in order to control the light and prevent the reaction from being too vigorous. But I'm not sure about other times when it might be important to keep them completely dark.",0.0,0.0,0.0,0.15991807148510484,,"Skipped (strategy=GUIDED_DISCOVERY, not intervention)",6,644
