else: There seems to be some confusion about how many different colors can form depending on various factors such as temperature changes during the experiment. Not all possible combinations will lead to observations of both blood red and prussian blue at room temperature within one experiment duration.",0.0,0.0,0.0,0.0,,"Skipped (strategy=GUIDED_DISCOVERY, not intervention)",8,767
