AFFIRM_AND_TRANSITION,✅,False,"""好的老师，我会非常小心地将点燃的火柴靠近导管口，确保氢气能被点燃。请您放心，我会随时注意安全。""","[""Insert(tool=match_1, vessel=delivery_tube_1, position=mouth)""]",你已经成功点燃了氢气，那么如果我们想要收集氢气燃烧后的产物，你觉得应该如何操作？比如，烧杯应该如何与导管连接？你会关注烧杯内壁的哪些现象来判断产物的性质呢？,"good job! when you light the match and bring it close to the opening of the delivery tube, a spark will appear which indicates that hydrogen gas is being produced. Keep in mind though, never touch any other part of the setup with your hands as they might catch on fire. Now can we move onto the next step?",0.0,0.0,0.0,0.0,,"Skipped (strategy=AFFIRM_AND_TRANSITION, not intervention)",6,886
