REMEDIATION_DIRECTIVE,❌,False,"""老师，我现在就用蘸了浓硫酸的木棍去弄到另一根干净的木棍上，应该很快就能看到现象了吧！我等一下就观察。""","[""Detach(object=wood_stick_2)"", ""Transfer(from_vessel=wood_stick_2, to_vessel=wood_stick_1, volume=2.0ml)"", ""Wait(duration=5.0)""]",进度提示：你的容器 paper_1 已满足部分条件，但还【器材类型错误 (需 wood_stick)】。请务必用蘸取了浓硫酸的木棍，准确滴加到另一根干净的木棍上，并静置观察。,"your idea is interesting! However, in our experiment we need to make sure that the drops from the droper do not stick to the sides of the glassware and instead fall into the solution. Can you try doing that?",15.555555555555555,6.741573033707865,14.444444444444443,2.741951283994402,,"Skipped (strategy=REMEDIATION_DIRECTIVE, not intervention)",8,932
