REMEDIATION_DIRECTIVE,❌,False,"""啊，老师，我、我觉得……如果铝箔包得松，可能、可能会有光线从缝隙里照进去吧？那、那样试管里的反应就不算真正避光了……呃，应该是要让铝箔贴得特别紧，最好一圈圈缠好，别让光进来，这样避光组和见光组才有区别……不过我包的时候老是包不紧，手一抖就松了……""",[],请立刻将铝箔包裹在 test_tube_1 上，确保 aluminum_foil 和 test_tube_1 之间建立连接。只有这样，避光组的对照才算完成。,"if the aluminum foil is not wrapped very well, it may allow some light to enter into the test-tube and affect the reaction. To make sure that the light does not enter, the aluminum foil should be wrapped very firm around the test-tube. The next step would be to proceed with the experiment.",21.455938697318004,19.305019305019304,21.455938697318004,7.73143337609087,,"Skipped (strategy=REMEDIATION_DIRECTIVE, not intervention)",6,1087
